videos.description: Liz Dixon shows off the sweet post moves as she puts in the layup right before the first-quarter buzzer.

videos.headline: Dixon's up-and-under beats the 1st-quarter buzzer for Louisville

videos.description: Hailey Van Lith finds Payton Verhulst for the 3-pointer, putting the Cardinals up 20 late in the second half.

videos.description: Shayeann Day-Wilson sets up an and-1, knocks down a 3-pointer and a layup to bring Duke within five in the fourth quarter.

videos.description: Louisville responds to Duke's 5-0 run by scoring seven straight, putting them up 12 in the fourth quarter.
